<script>
// import { fetchTable } from 'http/tableAPI';
import axios from 'axios'



export default {
  name: 'App',
  methods: {
    async fetchTable() {
      const $host = axios.create({
        baseURL: process.env.VUE_APP_API_URL
      })
      const {data} = await $host.get('api/table')
      console.log(data)
      return data
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    this.fetchTable()
  }
}
</script>
